</section>
<section id="diving-deeper-facets-and-multiple-geoms" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="diving-deeper-facets-and-multiple-geoms">Diving Deeper: Facets and Multiple Geoms</h2>
<p>Let’s create separate plots for each location and add a histogram of shark sightings:</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb6" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode r code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb6-1"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">ggplot</span>(ocean_temp, <span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;
