background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">"identity"</span>, <span class="at" style="color: #657422;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">alpha =</span> <span class="fl" style="color: #AD0000;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">0.3</span>)</span></code></pre></div>
</section>
